{"search_data": "RajasthanRajasthan Announces Farm Loan Waiver Scheme (Kisan Karz Mafi Yojna) for Farmers Rajasthan govt. announces Farm Loan Waiver Scheme (Kisan Karz Mafi Yojna) for farmers to waive off short term agricultural (crop) loans taken from cooperative banks, govt. also waived off loans upto Rs. 2 lakh taken from other banks, as on 30 November 2018, under Kisan Karj Mafi Yojana \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902This Karz Mafi Scheme in Rajasthan would resolve the agarian crisis and farmers distress in the state.Rajasthan Farm Loan Waiver Scheme (Kisan Karj Mafi Yojana)In the run up to the assembly elections, congress party has promised to waive off the farm loans of farmers within 10 days of coming to power. Now all the 3 states i.e Rajasthan, Madhya Pradesh & Chhattigarh have announced Kisan Karz Mafi Yojna. In Rajasthan Farmer Loan Waiver Scheme, govt. has write off all the short term crop loans taken by the farmers from cooperative banks.In addition to this, for the loans taken by the farmers from nationalized banks and other banks, the waiver would be for loans upto Rs. 2 lakh as on 30 November 2018. Kisan Karj Mafi Scheme will add an additional burden on the state exchequer but will provide a massive benefit to farmers who are in trouble and defaulted in loan payment.CM said that \u201cit is for the 1st time in the state that the farmers have committed suicide, situation is grave. So, the waiver would be for short term crop loans\u201d. Rajasthan Kisan Karz Mafi Yojna is expected to benefit around 23.5 lakh farmers in the state who had taken farm loans from cooperative banks.It's done!Rajasthan, Madhya Pradesh & Chhattisgarh have waived farm loans.We asked for 10 days.We did it in 2.\u2014 Rahul Gandhi (@RahulGandhi) December 19, 2018As per the official reports, cooperative banks lend farm loans of maximum of upto Rs. 1.5 lakh. Giving reaction on it, Rahul Gandi tweeted, \u201cWe did it\u201d. Previously, MP Farmer Loan Waiver Scheme and Chhattisgarh Farm Loan Waiver Scheme has been announced by the newly formed CM\u2019s in their respective states.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}